&lt;/dl></description></item><item><title>水、电解质代谢紊乱和酸碱平衡失调</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E6%B0%B4%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%A3%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E7%B4%8A%E4%B9%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%85%B8%E7%A2%B1%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E5%A4%B1%E8%B0%83/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 May 2022 22:07:35 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E6%B0%B4%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%A3%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E7%B4%8A%E4%B9%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%85%B8%E7%A2%B1%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E5%A4%B1%E8%B0%83/</guid><description>水、电解质代谢紊乱、酸碱平衡紊乱 渗透压正常范围为 280～310 mOsm/L。</description></item><item><title>输血</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%BE%93%E8%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 May 2022 23:25:23 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%BE%93%E8%A1%80/</guid><description>输血 输血的适应症 大量失血：人体总血量约 5000 ml，根据失血量选择输血方案。 &amp;lt; 10%：可自体代偿，无需输血； &amp;gt; 10%：适量晶体液、较体液或少量血浆</description></item><item><title>外科休克</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E4%BC%91%E5%85%8B/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 May 2022 14:12:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E4%BC%91%E5%85%8B/</guid><description>&lt;p>关于休克的详细内容，见&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E4%BC%91%E5%85%8B/">病理生理学-休克&lt;/a>。临床上常见的是低血容量性休克以及感染性休克（内毒素性休克）。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>麻醉</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 May 2022 22:11:18 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%A4%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
